Items.c: <[>哇！一顆糖都放幾年了,不壞掉才怪！這忠僕想珍惜少主恩賜之物,也該有個限度啊！<]>
Items.mt: <[>Wow! It's been a few years since a piece of candy went bad! This loyal servant wants to cherish the young master's gift, but he should have a limit! <]>
